{"tid":2014833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本共同社：解放軍8月進行模擬登陸東沙群島演習","createTime":"2020-05-13T09:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T09:41:01.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"944ec308af017b9863b70ab8e673634c0d485778","tid":2014833,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:14:11.000Z","msg":"共同社報道，中國軍方計劃8月在南海區域，進行模擬登陸東沙群島的大規模演習，將動用登陸艦、氣墊船、直升機和陸戰隊。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，東沙群島位於海南島經台灣南方的巴士海峽前往太平洋的路線上，對中國軍方進入太平洋海域的戰略上很重要。報道形容，中方對美軍在南海軍事活動日益活躍感到焦躁，今次模擬演習有可能導致與美台之間的緊張加劇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525647-20200512.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525647-20200512.htm&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=ca7f17ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1525647-20200512.htm&h=d6120ff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1525647-20200512.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0d1d4657e0a764453457c3f7b5c3777dc7f21541","tid":2014833,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"快D打仗 等唔切了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ca970f59b362840da7db2e4eb1298902235837","tid":2014833,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:16:49.000Z","msg":"今次一定要真打 唔好渣流灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba19a13764e2c512d0724cf995b7f48d8288b2f2","tid":2014833,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"打東沙係未即係對台宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f014c0dbfe8be63a91b6ec9ba1d06793563084","tid":2014833,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba19a13764e2c512d0724cf995b7f48d8288b2f2","tid":2014833,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc